# Matter Light na ESP32-C6 - Struktura Projektu

## Adresářová struktura

```
matter-light-esp32c6/
├── CMakeLists.txt                    # Top-level projekt CMakeLists
├── main/
│   ├── CMakeLists.txt
│   └── main.c                        # Main aplikace
├── components/
│   ├── led_driver/                   # Custom LED komponenta
│   │   ├── CMakeLists.txt
│   │   ├── include/
│   │   │   └── led_driver.h
│   │   └── led_driver.c
│   └── matter_config/                # Matter konfigurační komponenta
│       ├── CMakeLists.txt
│       └── matter_config.h
├── sdkconfig
├── sdkconfig.defaults
└── partitions.csv
```

## 1. Top-level CMakeLists.txt

```cmake
cmake_minimum_required(VERSION 3.16)
include($ENV{IDF_PATH}/tools/cmake/project.cmake)
project(matter_light_esp32c6)
```

## 2. main/CMakeLists.txt

```cmake
idf_component_register(
    SRCS "main.c"
    INCLUDE_DIRS "."
    REQUIRES "esp-matter" "led_driver" "led_strip" "nvs_flash" "esp_wifi" 
    PRIV_REQUIRES "esp_netif" "esp_event"
)
```

## 3. components/led_driver/CMakeLists.txt

```cmake
idf_component_register(
    SRCS "led_driver.c"
    INCLUDE_DIRS "include"
    REQUIRES "led_strip" "esp_common"
)
```

## 4. components/matter_config/CMakeLists.txt

```cmake
idf_component_register(
    INCLUDE_DIRS "."
)
```

